<h1 style="color:red;"><b>Test Your Understanding</b></h1>
</div>

<p>
For each chapter, we have developed a <span style="color:red;">test</span> to help you evaluate your
understanding of the basic concepts and techniques covered in that
chapter.
</p>

<p>
Each chapter test is composed of <span style="color:red;">five questions</span>, selected randomly
from a large set of questions associated with that chapter. Hence the
test <span style="color:red;">may be retaken multiple times</span>.
</p>

<p>
<span style="color:red;">Your Score:</span> For each question, if you answer it correctly on your
first attempt, you receive 20 points. A correct answer on the second
attempt yields 10 points, and no points are realized after the second attempt.
